		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does anyone think the Power Rangers is racist? They made the Red ranger Native American, the Black ranger African American, the Yellow ranger is (a girl) from East Asia...<br /><br />I'm surprised they didn't call the white guy the White ranger...after all, they made the other girl Pink...oh I get it Blue=boy, Pink=girl.<br /><br />I feel like a well know Feminist blogger should do an episode about that. And don't correct me for clarity, mods, I write specifically obscurely...to not have my posts linked to by Google searches for a subject which I don't want to be attached to.

		

